stagitbuild
===========

Builder - manager for you stagit page.


Description
-----------

stagitbuild generates a configuration file that you can 
fill in order to not deal with writing hook-scripts to 
get it to work. It works pretty straight-forward.


Installation
------------
You can install the script with (if necessary as root):

	make install

and start using the script right away.


Configuration
-------------
The script reads the generated configuration from
~/.stagitconf , which explains all the configuration
options. More detailed information is in the man page.

Dependencies
------------

* git
* stagit
* (optional) rsync [for syncing git repo to another place]
